Summary:
This role provides information about the processor architecture.

The role results in a numeric value whose meaning is written in curly braces:

```
0 { x86 }
1 { MIPS }
2 { Alpha }
3 { PowerPC }
5 { ARM }
6 { Itanium-based systems (ia64) }
9 { AMD64 }
12 { ARM64 }
default { Unknown architecture }
```
